Heavenly Creatures;;83;;93;;R;;Wealthy and precocious teenager Juliet (Kate Winslet) transfers from England to Christchurch, New Zealand, with her family, and forms a bond with the quiet, brooding Pauline (Melanie Lynskey) through their shared love of handsome big screen tenor Mario Lanza and games of make believe. But when their parents begin to suspect that their increasingly intense friendship is becoming unhealthy, the girls decide to run away to America, hatching a dark plan for those who threaten to keep them apart.;;Mystery & thriller;;Peter Jackson;;1994;;Melanie Lynskey,Kate Winslet,Sarah Peirse,Diana Kent,Clive Merrison,Simon O'Connor;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/heavenly_creatures